{"tid":1651785,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(戰略討論)如何應對臥底狗","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T13:18:28.000Z","uid":153617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a42def07bc0c54215c597aa8d8885231e189e3c9","tid":1651785,"uid":153617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"無可否認，臥底狗嘅出現，已經令好多人唔敢出，尤其是和理非，因為增加左被捕風險。我唔係做消極撚，而係想提出呢個問題，睇下有咩方法解決。<br />\n<br />\n我認為其中一個方法，係增加臥底狗出黎嘅恐懼同成本，令佢地唔敢再做臥底狗混入手捉當中。當然，我地唔應該過份分心喺現場捉鬼，但一旦捉到狗，一定要佢地有永久殘障，例如手,腳,耳,眼，個人就認為首選係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">眼</span></span>#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#do嗑g，話曬都嗌左還眼咁耐......"},{"pid":"a2af6b2e64a4c33d525f9ed79c17e38fe8043cc0","tid":1651785,"uid":153617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256622047ec0b8a6242a9646d6a78254d30ba4ef","tid":1651785,"uid":153617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b5139b67a99490263ac67a1c1ade05f034405c0","tid":1651785,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"119e91379f3a66290299d25f7fa6a3d433ffbe15","tid":1651785,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947ab33eb5da9495d3f650f0621048b875013c43","tid":1651785,"uid":286564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:18:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定要狠狠的還以顏色<br />\n打斷手腳成為廢人<br />\n還黑警警示<br />\n完全是以彼之道還施彼身</span></strong>"}]}